schools.name: Schulze Academy for Technology and Arts

data.description: Charming colonial located in the historic Bagley neighborhood in Detroit- west of University District & minutes away from the University of Detroit Mercy! Beautiful hardwood floors throughout with semi-open concept living. Tons of natural light through the bay window that highlights the gorgeous natural fireplace. The living room opens up to the nicely sized dining room that offers direct access to the backyard & covered porch. Updated kitchen with designer painted cabinets, and ample counter space. The second floor includes 3 bedrooms - one of which has a welcoming balcony. Hardwood flooring in the hallway & carpet throughout all bedrooms.
